strings: <voice_0x01000C69><se_high>tree: Well, that's me, that's Emma the maid.
<voice_0x01000C6A><se_high>tree: Looks like you haven't eaten the dinner that I brought you.
<voice_0x01000C6C><se_high>tree: Please reply, I want to make sure that everything is ok.
<voice_0x01000C6D><se_high>tree: ... there are? sorry for leaving you alone
